message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and valued at $12000 to you. Considering its high quality and unique features, I believe it would greatly benefit your operations or personal endeavors. I am offering this exceptional product to you at a special introductory price of $11000. This is an opportunity not to be missed, as it represents a significant savings compared to the standard retail price. I look forward to hearing your decision soon.
